version_description:
Important: Minimum supported server version is now 5.24.0. This may effect appliance users.

Features & Improvements:
- Support for Bookmarks
- Support for Birst Pro Edition Trial
- Share Annotations, now with dashboard metadata
- New "Run Now" option for email notifications
- Barcode scanner
- GPS location support in Geomaps
- Support for changing expired password if your session expires in app
